== 烹調 ==
將切片餡料用油煎炸，逐層添加番茄醬和起司，再用烤箱烘烤。某些版本會將餡料沾裹蛋液和麵粉（或麵包粉）再煎炸。有些食譜選用硬質的起司粉如：[[帕馬森乾酪|帕馬森起司]]；有些選用軟質會融化的起司，如：[[莫薩里拉乾酪|莫札瑞拉起司]]，或者兩種起司都用。

== 各國差異 ==
裹粉炸肉排的變化版如：使用[[小牛肉|小牛肉]]和[[雞肉|雞肉]]的千層焗烤，在許多國家都很受歡迎，特別是義大利移民區。

焗烤千層小牛肉或焗烤千層雞肉，在美國和加拿大常當作主菜，有時會做成[[潛艇三明治|潛艇三明治]]。也是[[意式麵食|意式麵食]]常見的配菜。有時會加入炒過（或生的）洋蔥丁或[[菜椒|青椒]]丁。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.foodnetwork.com/recipes/cooking-live/veal-parmigiana-recipe/index.html|title=Veal Parmigiana Recipe|accessdate=2014-03-23|date=<!--undated-->|last=Ostrosky|first=Marie|publisher=Food Network|archive-date=2014-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140107205732/http://www.foodnetwork.com/recipes/cooking-live/veal-parmigiana-recipe/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 波隆那炸豬排（Cotolette alla Bolognese）是義大利另一道類似的小牛肉菜餚，但傳統義大利 <ref>{{cite web|url=http://italianfood.about.com/od/beefbracioleetc/r/blr0229.htm|title=Veal Parmigiana Recipe – Cotolette alla Bolognese – Easy Veal Parmigiana Recipe|accessdate=2014-03-23|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|date=2014-03-03|last=Phillips|first=Kyle|publisher=Italianfood.about.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712164720/http://italianfood.about.com/od/beefbracioleetc/r/blr0229.htm|archivedate=2014-07-12}}</ref> 食譜中不含番茄醬。另一道相關的小牛肉菜餚是「Costelette Parmigiana」，但是在義大利通常不會加醬或起司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.chowhound.com/food-news/53553/fake-accent/|title=Fake Accent|accessdate=November 1, 2015|date=October 12, 2006|last=Kaminski|first=Margot|website={{tsl|en|Chowhound||Chowhound}}|archive-date=2019-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520053517/https://www.chowhound.com/food-news/53553/fake-accent/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

焗烤千層小牛肉或雞肉在澳洲和[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]很常見，配菜是薯條或沙拉。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/the-daily-meal/americas-best-chicken-par_b_3437241.html|title=America's Best Chicken Parm Sandwiches|accessdate=14 May 2014|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|date=13 June 2013|work=The Huffington Post|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930014721/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/the-daily-meal/americas-best-chicken-par_b_3437241.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://weblogs.clarin.com/revistaenie-nerdsallstar/2012/05/11/milanesa_napolitana/|title=Milanesa napolitana|last=Pisarro|first=Marcelo|date=2012-05-11|newspaper={{tsl|en|Clarín (Argentine newspaper)||Clarín (Argentine newspaper)}}|location=Buenos Aires, Argentina|language=es|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517140858/http://weblogs.clarin.com/revistaenie-nerdsallstar/2012/05/11/milanesa_napolitana/|archive-date=2014-05-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 這道菜在澳洲可能有多種配料，例如火腿片或煎[[茄|茄子]]片。<ref name="Levin2004-08-07">{{cite news|url=http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/08/04/1091557910488.html|title=Keeping abreast of the Parma best|last=Levin|first=Darren|date=2004-08-07|newspaper=[[世纪报|The Age]]|location=Melbourne, Victoria|page=A2.2|accessdate=2016-12-29|archive-date=2012-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121011230155/http://www.theage.com.au/articles/2004/08/04/1091557910488.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Peucker2001-01-02">{{cite news|url=http://www.news.com.au/national/the-parmi-police/story-e6frfkp9-1225980130317|title=They're the parmi police Duo in quest for Adelaide's best|last=Peucker|first=Christie|date=2011-01-02|newspaper={{tsl|en|Sunday Mail (Adelaide)||Sunday Mail}}|location=Adelaide, South Australia|page=20|accessdate=2016-12-29|archive-date=2015-08-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150815023432/http://www.news.com.au/national/the-parmi-police/story-e6frfkp9-1225980130317|dead-url=no}}</ref>

阿根廷和其他南美鄰近國家，焗烤千層小牛肉或雞肉會佐以火腿和薯條，稱為「 milanesa a la napolitana」。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://weblogs.clarin.com/revistaenie-nerdsallstar/2012/05/11/milanesa_napolitana/|title=Milanesa napolitana|date=2012-05-11|last=Pisarro|first=Marcelo|language=es|newspaper={{tsl|en|Clarín (Argentine newspaper)||Clarín (Argentine newspaper)}}|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517140858/http://weblogs.clarin.com/revistaenie-nerdsallstar/2012/05/11/milanesa_napolitana/|archive-date=2014-05-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.elreporte.com.uy/milanesa-a-la-napolitana/|title=Milanesa a la napolitana|date=2013-04-25|language=es|website=El Reporte|author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.-->|accessdate=2016-12-29|archive-date=2021-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211109164016/https://www.elreporte.com.uy/milanesa-a-la-napolitana/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abc.com.py/edicion-impresa/suplementos/gastronomia/el-origen-de-la-milanesa-557404.html |title=El origen de la milanesa |date=2013-04-13 |newspaper={{tsl|en|Diario ABC Color||ABC Color}} |language=es |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517151454/http://www.abc.com.py/edicion-impresa/suplementos/gastronomia/el-origen-de-la-milanesa-557404.html |archivedate=2014-05-17 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://elgranchef.imujer.com/6386/clasica-milanesa-napolitana-de-argentina|title=Clásica milanesa napolitana de Argentina|date=2012-07-13|last=Asier|first=Soren|language=es|website=iMujer|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618030822/http://elgranchef.imujer.com/6386/clasica-milanesa-napolitana-de-argentina|dead-url=no}}</ref> 如果加上煎蛋，這道菜就是「<span>súper milanesa」</span> 或者「<span>suprema napolitana</span>」。在1940年代，布宜諾斯艾利斯的一間拿坡里餐廳創作了這道菜。

有一道英國菜餚稱為「parmo」，只用豬肉或雞肉，也類似焗烤千層茄子。

焗烤千層在巴西是熱門餐點，由義大利移民將其發揚光大（巴西的義大利移民人口全球最多）。巴西有三種千層焗烤：焗烤千層雞排（<span>filé de frango a parmigiana</span> ）、焗烤千層茄子（<span>berinjela a parmigiana</span>）、焗烤肉排千層（<span>meat parmigiana）</span>。肉排有三種牛肉部位，包括兩種極佳級部位：焗烤千層菲力牛排（<span>filé mignon à parmigiana</span>）、焗烤千層沙朗牛排（<span>contra-filé à parmigiana）</span>，而第三種「{{tsl|pt|Bife à parmegiana|bife à parmegiana}}<span>」，</span>用的就是非特定部位的牛肉。巴西的焗烤千層搭配的不是白米飯和炸馬鈴薯，就是配義大利麵食加番茄醬。

